{"tid":825973,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"楊思琦貼舊相老作，被網民踢爆恥笑刪帖了事","createTime":"2018-09-18T02:21:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T13:43:26.000Z","uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"237919ce6bbd1b04f72281bc01a8660ba012eba1","tid":825973,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T02:21:00.000Z","msg":"楊思琦貼舊相老作，被網民踢爆恥笑刪帖了事<br />\n<br />\n山竹襲港，好多人受影響，但楊思琦真搞笑，竟然係大陸微博發澳門寰宇天下舊年天鴿爆玻璃條片，話係自己香港屋企對面樓😅😅😅<br />\n<br />\n最好笑係條舊片入面個男人仲好大聲話寰宇天下，香港邊有寰宇天下呀？結果俾網民話佢想抽山竹水，實情係點就唔知喇，結果搞到刪帖收場&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/102019_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F102019_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=7524ff0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/102020_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F102020_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=887078d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b147994c742193533994ebe5344370a823e4a723","tid":825973,"uid":142313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T02:22:36.000Z","msg":"屌爆楊思琦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04ab54872ac2e7eaea80926dc28981e991619f9d","tid":825973,"uid":16567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T02:23:55.000Z","msg":"大話老雞"},{"pid":"70b3a98b17652e0a1dd070950bbd5cc4393f935d","tid":825973,"uid":16567,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"b147994c742193533994ebe5344370a823e4a723","tid":825973,"uid":142313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T02:22:36.000Z","msg":"屌爆楊思琦<img src=\"/assets/fac